    <briefdescription>
<para>Helper macros for specializing the std::hash. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This group provides a util <ref refid="structeu_1_1core_1_1HashCombiner" kindref="compound">HashCombiner</ref> to simplify the creation of hash functions for user-defined types (using std::hash) and macros for specialization of std::hash for custom types.</para>
<para>Example usage: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group__hash_1ga9038dc1dac99b31ae58ae04bee68d416" kindref="member">HASH_DEF_BEGIN</ref>(<ref refid="structeu_1_1R" kindref="compound">MyType</ref>)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="group__hash_1ga102a60c28b17bc852589bbb26135173b" kindref="member">HASH_DEF</ref>(<ref refid="structeu_1_1R" kindref="compound">member1</ref>)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="group__hash_1ga102a60c28b17bc852589bbb26135173b" kindref="member">HASH_DEF</ref>(<ref refid="structeu_1_1R" kindref="compound">member2</ref>)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group__hash_1gadea525dabdf353ba96abce59e6a5dadd" kindref="member">HASH_DEF_END</ref>()</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
